"tail":", inserted “(including a microloan, as defined by the Secretary)” after “A direct loan” in introductory provisions."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (e). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/79/s5105"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–79, § 5105","children":[],"tail":", added subsec. (e)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1996—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/127"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–127","children":[],"tail":" amended section generally, substituting present provisions for provisions outlining purposes of loans made under this subchapter, authorizing loans to rural area residents to operate small business enterprises, authorizing loans for pollution abatement and control projects in rural areas and providing for limitations on such loans, and authorizing creation, from loan funds, of nonsupervised bank accounts to be used at discretion of borrower for necessary family living expenses."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1992—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/552/s516/f/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–552, § 516(f)(2)","children":[],"tail":", repealed amendment by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/237/s501/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–237, § 501(b)","children":[],"tail":". See 1991 Amendment note below."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/552/s516/f/1/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–552, § 516(f)(1)(A)","children":[],"tail":", made technical correction to directory language of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/624/s1818/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–624, § 1818(b)","children":[],"tail":". See 1990 Amendment note below."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1991—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/237/s501/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–237, § 501(b)","children":[],"tail":", which directed the substitution of “systems (for purposes of this subchapter, th